* [List any factors or barriers that are impeding the client's recovery and return to work. These may include psychological factors (e.g., persistent symptoms, fear of returning to work, avoidance behaviours), practical factors (e.g., workplace issues, lack of suitable duties, transport difficulties), social factors (e.g., lack of family support, financial stress), or other relevant factors mentioned in the transcripts or documents. If no barriers have been identified, print "Unknown."]


